- Initial Install via USB
  - Storage Settings (for ZFS Pool)
    - Swap - 0
    - Root - 465
    - Minfree - 0
    - Maxvz - 0
  - Storage Settings (for local install)
    - Swap - 0
    - Root - <disk size>
    - Minfree - 0
    - Maxvz - 0
  - Locale Settings
    - United States
    - America/Denver
  - IP Settings
    - <node>.<domain.tld>
    - IP - 10.x.x.x
    - Gateway - 10.x.x.x
    - DNS - 1.1.1.1 (default upstream to Cloudflare DNS)


- Post Install 
  - Resize Partitions
    - lvresize -l +100%FREE /dev/pve/root
    - resize2fs /dev/mapper/pve-root
    - df -h # check that changes applied -> make sure /dev/mapper/pve-root shows the correct size
  - Fix Apt Repositories
    - cd /etc/apt/sources.list.d
    - nano ceph -> add # in front
    - nano pve-enterprise.list -> add # in front
    - cd /etc/apt/
    - nano sources.list -> add 'deb http://download.proxmox.com/debian/pve bookworm pve-no-subscription'
  - Update Repositories and Apply Updates
    - apt update && apt upgrade -y
  - Install Packages
    - apt install unattended-upgrades -y
    - apt install ufw -y
    - apt install fail2ban - y
    - apt install openvswitch-switch -y
    - apt install ntfs-3g -y
    - apt install grub-efi-amd64 -y (mini pcs)
  - Restore Network Configuration
    - See file
    - systemctl restart networking (wait about 15-30 secs for configuration to reload)
  - Configure Firewall
    - ufw allow 8006/tcp comment 'for webgui'
    - ufw allow 22/tcp comment 'for ssh'
    - ufw enable
  - Configure ZFS Pool
    - Create ZFS Pool with Single Disk, ashift=12, compression=on
    - zpool import -f ZFS_Pool (for import)
  - Join Cluster
  - Configure ACME Certs for TLS
    - Create ACME Account
    - Setup Cloudflare DNS Plugin
    - Add server to ACME Account
    - Order Certs

** Once all cluster nodes are added **
  - Setup MFA for Login -> Duo or Microsoft Auth
  - Import Backups
    - mkdir /mnt/backup_drive
    - fdisk -l # to find external drive
    - mount -t ntfs-3g /dev/sdx1 /mnt/backup_drive
    - cp * /mnt/backup_drive/folder_to_backups/ /var/lib/vz/dump
  - Upload ISOs
    - Windows22H2.iso
    - ubuntu-server-22.04-LTS
    - ubuntu-server-24.04-LTS
  - Restore VMs/CTs from Backup from /var/lib/vz/dump
